title: Kubernetes: Node and Cluster Level Network Usage
agents: kubernetes
catalog: containerization/kubernetes
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check and the associated special agent (agent_kubernetes) are deprecated
 and will be removed in Checkmk version 2.2.0.

 Please configure the new special agent using the "Kubernetes" ruleset.

 This check monitors at cluster and node level the network interfaces. It
 gives the link speed, packet counts, discards and errors.

item:
 The network interface that is monitored

discovery:
 One service is created for each network interface.
